\f1\fs28 \cf3 \cb4 The synth-leather of Leo\'92s new shoes squeaked faintly against the perfectly clean pavement, a satisfying sound in the otherwise ambient hum of the city morning. He glanced down, admiring the way the iridescent material caught the perpetually pleasant sunlight.\'a0
